atAGlanceFacts.factValue: Baseboard, Hot Water, Natural Gas, Pellet Stove

data.description: This delightful 2.45-acre property offers the perfect balance between country living and the convenience of the city. Step into this welcoming ranch-style home with a loft. This home features a family room and a living room for gatherings and relaxation. The spacious rustic kitchen is the heart of this home, ideal for hosting friends and family for memorable meals.   A pellet stove in the living room ensures cozy warmth during cool fall and winter evenings. Newer windows throughout not only enhance energy efficiency but also elevate the home's overall appeal. Home features 3 bedrooms, 2 ½ bath, living room, family room and a loft. Property currently zoned SFR-4 with development potentials. Call for your personal showing.
